<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Balaji S - Profile</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b, #2563eb);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .profile-card {
            width: 900px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 40px;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .profile-img {
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 5px solid #60a5fa;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 38px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin-top: 25px;
        }
        
        .section h2 {
            color: #60a5fa;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #60a5fa;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .section ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .section li {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .skills span {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #2563eb;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="profile-card">

        <div class="header">
            <img src="profile.png" alt="Balaji" class="profile-img">
            <h1>Balaji S</h1>
            <p>B.Tech - Information Technology</p>
        </div>
        <div class=" section ">
            <h2>🎓 Education</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>College:</strong> KCG College of Technology</li>
                <li><strong>Degree:</strong> B.Tech - Information Technology (IT)</li>
                <li><strong>Year:</strong> 3rd Year</li>
                <li>Passionate about Software Development, Web Development, and Emerging Technologies.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>


        <div class="section ">
            <h2>💻 Skills</h2>
            <div class="skills ">
                <span>Java</span>
                <span>HTML</span>
                <span>CSS</span>
                <span>Problem Solving</span>
                <span>Web Development</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section ">
            <h2>🎯 Hobbies</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>📚 Reading Books</li>
                <li>🎌 Watching Anime</li>
                <li>🎮 Playing Story-Based Games</li>
                <li>🚀 Exploring New Technologies</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="section ">
            <h2>🌟 About Me</h2>
            <p>
                Hello! I am <b>Balaji S</b>, a 3rd Year B.Tech Information Technology student at <b>KCG College of Technology</b>. I am passionate about programming, web development, and learning new technologies. My hobbies include reading books, watching
                anime, and playing unique story-based games. My goal is to become a skilled software engineer and contribute to innovative technology solutions.
            </p>
        </div>


        <div class="footer ">
            © 2026 Balaji S | Future Software Engineer
        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>